snippet.title: Titan Hunters Gameplay
snippet.description:
TITAN HUNTERS is inspired by fun gameplay of Diablo, Voxel’s signature look and the feel of Minecraft. It is a creative and unique game project that combines NFT (Earning Nature) and the best gaming genre of MMORPG (Fun Nature).
In TITAN HUNTERS, you can become a hunter discover secrets in an exciting world of miracles and mysteries. Gamers can also participate in epic battles to fight angry and cunning monster bosses – Titans. Hunt alone or team up with other players and use materials collected from fallen foes to craft new gear and take on even bigger, badder Titan!

https://www.titanhunters.io/
